text: Hava Mustafa (; born 20 September 1997) is a Macedonian footballer who plays as a forward for 1. liga club ŽFK Shkëndija and the North Macedonia women's national team. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Macedonian women's footballers Category:North Macedonia women's international footballers
